      <title>市场考虑关税风险，欧洲天然气价格波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲天然气价格波动，交易商评估了美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税威胁再次引发贸易战担忧的情况下，未来一年供应可能吃紧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 07:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银与多家银行联手暂停新世界证券的保证金贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ubs-halts-margin-loans-on-some-new-world-development-securities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，瑞银集团停止接受新世界发展有限公司部分债券和股票作为保证金贷款的抵押品，加入其他全球银行的行列，暂停向富有客户提供此类融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ubs-halts-margin-loans-on-some-new-world-development-securities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 05:57:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
